All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class FedExAPIException
extends java.lang.Exception

This class defines a general exception that the API can throw because of any of a number of conditions. The specific condition will be represented by the code and sometimes also by a detail message that can be retrieved with the getMessage() method. Most of the integer values that the code can take are defined here.
